Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自古以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们就对妖怪心存畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而妖怪们的统帅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领军「百鬼夜行」的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们称之为妖怪的总帅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赋予其别称
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魑魅魍魉之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「滑头鬼」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉章就像老夫年轻的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要被「畏」惧 一直想成为妖怪们的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和被称为「七人同行」的妖怪们一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「七人同行 」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干部之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫犬神的家伙十分危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是家伙借由聚集怨恨和愤恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以提升自身力量的可怕妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突如其来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在陆生他们面前出现的的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}大家 从这里出去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐神刑部狸 玉章和其部下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「七人同行」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们公然与奴良组和陆生拉开战线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取奴良组的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了他们征服全国的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去 我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾想要融入人类社会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力地在模仿人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为我生为妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不认同我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不曾接受过我 如此活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我 连妖怪世界的存在都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都没有我的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到那天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fad(200,0)\bord3\be4\3c&H27275F&}拉开暗夜的帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恨 好恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恨奴良陆生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头 头居然...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神廉贞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神改造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人式一体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开花院阴阳术「黄泉送葬水泡枪（柚罗MAX！）」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更换了灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经没问题了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 回礼堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了能映出妖怪的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要是妖怪真的出现了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是有这把百济七支刀在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来给我捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 不会再让你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 尽会玩些小伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这种破绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的线越是挣扎勒得越紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首无的线可不是泛泛之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我第一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了妖怪也有像人类那样的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你成为我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你也是妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是同伴 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这样......
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我非得遭遇这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想见识一下你的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有什么力量......
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小的妖怪没有生存的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正活下去也只能是被人类蔑视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回到那边去吗 还是......
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟大家聚在一块儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人吃惊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种越是充满憎恶越是强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来吧 让你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你见识下一个崭新的妖怪世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉章对既非人类又非妖怪的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我当成一个真正的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉章 四国妖怪的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有玉章 才能聚集真的「畏」 成为百妖之主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的器量完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和人类混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不起眼地隐藏身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙 即便在人类之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是耀眼的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以力量征服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连人类也可以支配
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和被随从保护 跟人类嬉笑打闹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意忘形的你完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被玉章欺骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉章是只披着貘皮的狸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我一开始就明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样 玉章
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪比人类高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我也有归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是他教会我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类与妖怪不分高低贵贱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才没有错！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什……什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能阻止因愤怒而觉醒出新力量的犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认可我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有玉章他们认可我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们哪儿都没有做错！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认可你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种跟任何人都亲近的妖怪 我决不认可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 这绳子不会那么轻易就被弄断的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 请退下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是玉章的忠心部下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没点动静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼堂好像很喧闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛 你去看下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在修理这个仪器 腾不出空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去谁去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 就会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 那里原来没有破的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清继 出现了 出现了 有妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 真的出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我 礼堂里有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我现在马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆生少爷 请退后一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无首 这家伙到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然变得这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头回到身体上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛同学 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门开不了 岛同学 岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被混凝土块绊住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 岛同学 岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护陆生少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些死不足惜的妖怪怎能阻挡我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主请快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我们……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛同学！岛同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不会有人来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了奴良陆生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拉开帷幕的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点从舞台上滚下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白目演员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 少主您平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 是奴良陆生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚给了你点颜色 你就开染坊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你是谁都无所谓 我只要把你宰了就成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是误认为身体越大就越强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少给我在那里说风凉话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种软脚虾怎么可能有强大的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会认同你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛同学！ 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清继同学 礼堂里有妖怪……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧 让我以这百济七支刀……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由本清十字怪奇侦探团团长来消灭他！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们尽快离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再四处逃窜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这妖怪也就只有这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要分个实力高下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是个目光短浅的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种半吊子的妖怪 一抓一大把啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎会被你…… 被你这家伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬神 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是重要的伙伴 现在还不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这演这出没用的戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是奴良陆生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会变得如此威风凛凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来也不必要再玩些袭击人类什么的小把戏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如我之前说过的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要夺取你的「畏」 立于百妖之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话我原封不动的还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 今天我们就此退散了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过下次再见时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是将你的「畏」与你的命收于我手之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐身刑部狸玉章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是会演戏的一只狸猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶犬亮出其獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与玉章之间的战斗 已迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 马头丸 这本书你也有一本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《我所爱的奴良组》？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛鬼大人自费出版的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖不出吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来就不好卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 滑头鬼之孙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七分三分的誓言之酒
